<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 relative">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">About Me</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold font-display tracking-tight">My Background &amp; Expertise</p>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1 w-12 rounded bg-teal-500"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      
      <!-- Biography & Details -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg">
        <p>
          I am a passionate <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Software Engineering student</strong> at TAR UMT, currently pursuing my Bachelor's degree. My primary focus lies in backend development, systems architecture, and crafting scalable, robust full-stack solutions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Throughout my academic and professional journey, I have developed solid capabilities in <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Java, Spring Boot, Angular, and RESTful API design</strong>. I enjoy solving complex problems, working on database optimization, and implementing secure web applications.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am highly driven by the principles of clean code, Agile engineering methodologies, and continuous learning. With experience in fintech solutions and smart web systems, I thrive in collaborative environments where I can leverage technology to solve real-world problems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Stats Sidebar -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Quick Facts</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 rounded bg-teal-500/10 dark:bg-teal-400/15 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Education</h4>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">TAR UMT — Bachelor of Computer Science in Software Engineering (Honors)</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 rounded bg-teal-500/10 dark:bg-teal-400/15 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Key Skills</h4>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Java, Spring Boot, Angular, MySQL, Git, REST APIs</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 rounded bg-teal-500/10 dark:bg-teal-400/15 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Focus Areas</h4>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Enterprise Applications, API Integrations, Database Systems, Cloud Computing</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 rounded bg-teal-500/10 dark:bg-teal-400/15 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Location</h4>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
